{"tid":30463,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"宇宙雖有其起源，卻沒有終結—— 無限。","createTime":"2016-12-09T07:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T12:50:06.000Z","uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c306e7a14f70bacafd826687d62fd081809fa923","tid":30463,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"宇宙雖有其起源，卻沒有終結&mdash;&mdash;無限。<br />\n星球也有起源，卻因其自身之力走向毀滅&mdash;&mdash;有限。<br />\n歷史上擁有智慧的人類往往是最愚昧的。<br />\n生活在海中的魚不知道陸地的存在，如果它們擁有智慧也會走向毀滅。<br />\n人類如果想要超越光速，比魚類生活在陸地更為滑稽。<br />\n這就是，對於反抗神人們的&mdash;&mdash;最後通牒。"},{"pid":"920fdb6fbba08cf41d57ff4a06591f7c335b66d8","tid":30463,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"人被殺就會死"},{"pid":"c55a63bf2e46ff5206d8f62cfb39bf013530d1de","tid":30463,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"好期待Steins Gate 0 動畫化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40fd184f53a30e3f737feb933c6ccd29c5b0481","tid":30463,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人被殺就會死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Dh8W8q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Dh8W8q.jpg&h=69b29ebd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60f63852c1a00e8c6f360bbfd9639d0340b7e858","tid":30463,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好期待Steins Gate 0 動畫化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"