&h=69b29ebd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.17dm.com//img/pic/101120/7420_161238_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.17dm.com%2F%2Fimg%2Fpic%2F101120%2F7420_161238_1.jpg&h=69f1ec7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cf31b29e6174ea11138132d700fdc9380f0e43a","tid":30463,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好期待Steins Gate 0 動畫化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2017年一定有 放心</blockquote><br />\n好期待動畫點將2條世界線表達出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動畫版唔知點出<br />\n一個路線接一個路線，但時間點又一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGame 無將跳線原因講清，要自己推理，唔知動畫會唔會畫出腸表達出黎"},{"pid":"86c48e4cfefa265daa82197357ed9436d0266db3","tid":30463,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n好期待動畫點將2條世界線表達出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動畫版唔知點出<br />\n一個路線接一個路線，但時間點又一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGame 無將跳線原因講清，要自己推理，唔知動畫會唔會畫出腸表達出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初我都要上網自己睇翻個跳世界線原因<br />\n<br />\n而且條條角色線又有爆點"},{"pid":"0fd9bd2d7fc0565fd7ca67b7248d61972aad891c","tid":30463,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動畫版唔知點出<br />\n一個路線接一個路線，但時間點又一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGame 無將跳線原因講清，要自己推理，唔知動畫會唔會畫出腸表達出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初我都要上網自己睇翻個跳世界線原因<br />\n<br />\n而且條條角色線又有爆點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係講劇情章節路線唔係世界線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然有啲路線係一條完左回到過去又一條<br />\n但係如果係順住劇情走向播黎表達好似唔係幾夠喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f20c5089e40c8426c25c6498cb45df81e1955a7","tid":30463,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n好期待動畫點將2條世界線表達出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動畫版唔知點出<br />\n一個路線接一個路線，但時間點又一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGame 無將跳線原因講清，要自己推理，唔知動畫會唔會畫出腸表達出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初我都要上網自己睇翻個跳世界線原因<br />\n<br />\n而且條條角色線又有爆點</blockquote><br />\n無記錯唔同線既取決點係助手遺產落入邊個組織手上<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">俄羅斯/美軍/Stratfor/Sern，當中間接影響埋篝既命運</span></span><br />\n透過改變未來再間接改變過去，最後造成跳線"},{"pid":"7749f6c4086cd660e07ea61a77527ec233eb67b1","tid":30463,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動畫版唔知點出<br />\n一個路線接一個路線，但時間點又一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGame 無將跳線原因講清，要自己推理，唔知動畫會唔會畫出腸表達出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初我都要上網自己睇翻個跳世界線原因<br />\n<br />\n而且條條角色線又有爆點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係講劇情章節路線唔係世界線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然有啲路線係一條完左回到過去又一條<br />\n但係如果係順住劇情走向播黎表達好似唔係幾夠喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係共通線&gt; 助手線&gt; 嘟嘟嚕線 &gt;True End<br />\n助手線中間唔知會唔會插入真帆線，兩條線係同一個變動率互相連接"},{"pid":"1a29fb2aa68de5b8c3861eb0618c4497c210b6a6","tid":30463,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:29:47.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av1410387/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav1410387%2F&d=y7gdkFo918GblnQd%2F2QIJmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=abfb743e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av1410387/</a>"},{"pid":"686a53a08d3495fc4561f9f72cc537f4cd4d9199","tid":30463,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知大家有冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av1410387/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav1410387%2F&d=y7gdkFo918GblnQd%2F2QIJmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=abfb743e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av1410387/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好耐之前睇過 其中一條女好大波<br />\n唔記得邊個"},{"pid":"589a0312f33aefd7524c2471c3e5ed15878d160a","tid":30463,"uid":56277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"想睇かがり線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7138e1bd2cfacbded69940ce803bca920d15ae","tid":30463,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇かがり線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4691b6fb9a36524c445c1ec17f811e76f859447","tid":30463,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"屎坦因滋基度世界第一"}]}